ntributed content. If set to \"Strip disallowed tags\", dangerous tags are removed (see below). If set to \"Escape tags\", all HTML is escaped and presented as it was typed.','none'),(1634,' modules/filter/filter.module:671','default','If \"Strip disallowed tags\" is selected, optionally specify tags which should not be stripped. JavaScript event attributes are always stripped.','none'),(1635,' modules/filter/filter.module:675','default','Display HTML help','none'),(1636,' modules/filter/filter.module:677','default','If enabled, Drupal will display some basic HTML help in the long filter tips.','none'),(1637,' modules/filter/filter.module:681','default','Spam link deterrent','none'),(1638,' modules/filter/filter.module:683','default','If enabled, Drupal will add rel=\"nofollow\" to all links, as a measure to reduce the effectiveness of spam links. Note: this will also prevent valid links from being followed by search engines, therefore it is likely most effective when enabled for anonymous users.','none'),(1639,' modules/filter/filter.module:720','default','Maximum link text length','none'),(1640,' modules/filter/filter.module:723','default','URLs longer than this number of characters will be truncated to prevent long strings that break formatting. The link itself will be retained; just the text portion of the link will be truncated.','none'),(1641,' modules/filter/filter.module:153','default','administer filters','none'),(1642,' modules/filter/filter.module:90','default','Delete input format','6.9'),(1643,' modules/filter/filter.module:128','default','Rearrange','6.9'),(1644,' modules/filter/filter.module:0','default','filter','6.9'),(1645,' modules/filter/filter.install:14','default','Primary Key: Auto-incrementing filter ID.','6.4'),(1646,' modules/filter/filter.install:27','default','The origin module of the filter.','6.4'),(1647,' modules/filter/filter.install:34','default','ID to identify which filter within module is being referenced.','6.4'),(1648,' modules/